X Platform - Courses System Documentation
Overview

The Courses System is designed to organize educational content inside subjects.

Each subject can contain multiple courses, and each course belongs to one specific subject.

The system supports:

Admin-created courses
Teacher-created courses
Course resources/files
Published/unpublished course visibility
Future integration with lessons, access codes, and payments

The system is designed to scale later into a full paid educational platform.

Course Creation Policy

Courses can be created by:

Admin users
Teacher users

Students are NOT allowed to create or manage courses.

Teacher Assignment Rules
Admin Behavior

If an Admin creates a course:

→ Admin must choose the teacher responsible for the course

This allows centralized management of courses and teachers.

Teacher Behavior

If a Teacher creates a course:

→ The teacher is automatically assigned as the course teacher

Teachers cannot assign another teacher to their own course.

