Important Architecture Separation
Course Resources
CourseResource

Used for:

General course files
Lesson Resources (Future)
LessonResource

Will be used later for:

Files attached to specific lessons
Why This Separation Is Important

This architecture prevents confusion between:

Files for the whole course
Files for individual lessons

This improves:

Scalability
Clean database design
Future maintainability
